original_title":"वाइल्ड वाइल्ड पंजाब","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1252457,"adult":false,"title":"Vijay 69","video":false,"overview":"An adventurous, foul-mouthed former swimming coach reaches for record-breaking glory when he attempts a triathlon at 69 years old.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.4176,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/tSQzRaYyKEjM8gEyhqayU4rhbdU.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-08","vote_average":6.87,"backdrop_path":"/oU9WaOwdaxmO6HDKKVf5O3GnrO2.jpg","original_title":"विजय 69","original_language":"hi"},{"id":1599,"adult":false,"title":"I ♥ Huckabees","video":false,"overview":"A husband-and-wife team play detective, but not in the traditional sense. Instead, the happy duo helps others solve their existential issues, the kind that keep you up at night, wondering what it all means.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":4.0499,"vote_count":690,"poster_path":"/h27ytqXyOrAB6KmRx2abOp8p2W.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-10","vote_average":6.285,"backdrop_path":"/lMSlZxJp43HR81XacWh75w3hW2l.jpg","original_title":"I ♥ Huckabees","original_language":"en"},{"id":1832,"adult":false,"title":"Dogma","video":false,"overview":"An abortion clinic worker with a special heritage is called upon to save the existence of humanity from being negated by two renegade angels trying to exploit a loophole and reenter Heaven.","genre_ids":[14,35,12],"popularity":4.0798,"vote_count":2763,"poster_path":"/dXXhveI3VO51C3VNzNrxYl2xbST.jpg","release_date":"1999-10-04","vote_average":6.925,"backdrop_path":"/nljRWpjfmqh5qYxcblFoazU5eYY.jpg","original_title":"Dogma","original_language":"en"},{"id":1061230,"adult":false,"title":"Barati","video":false,"overview":"Sunder, a laid-back young man, cares nothing about responsibilities towards his own future or of his family's. At much persuasion by his widowed mother, Sunder leaves on a journey to find a suitable groom for his sister Laajo. Situations arises and Sunder ends up marrying Pilu, daughter of Mooley Shah from the neighboring village. Sunder's mother and maternal uncle Bishandas are happy for Sunder's marriage but are disappointed by Sunder's irresponsibility towards Laajo's marriage. This time Bishandas decides to accompany Sunder for a groom hunt. After a few attempts they find a boy for Laajo, Atmaram, a government employee. The marriage takes place, but Atmaram's father Lala Kedarnath asks for money as dowry. This puts Laajo's marriage in jeopardize. Finally, Bishandas manages to make Atmaram to disown his father and accept Laajo.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":3.1833,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/xd2JuXqxCyrdlA2Yj9Q7ejdVciL.jpg","release_date":"1954-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Barati","original_language":"hi"},{"id":272876,"adult":false,"title":"Anna Goldin, the Last Witch","video":false,"overview":"A native of Sennwald, Anna Göldi arrived in Glarus in 1765. For seventeen years, she worked as a maidservant for Johann Jakob Tschudi, a physician. Tschudi reported her for having put needles in the bread and milk of one of his daughters, apparently through supernatural means. Göldi at first escaped arrest, but the authorities of the Canton of Glarus advertised a reward for her capture in the Zürcher Zeitung on February 9, 1782. Göldi was arrested and under torture, admitted to entering in a pact with the Devil, who had appeared to her as a black dog. She withdrew her confession after the torture ended, but was sentenced on June 18, 1782 to execution by decapitation. The charges were officially of \"poisoning\" rather than witchcraft, even though the law at the time did not impose the death penalty for non-lethal poisoning.","genre_ids":[36,18,10770,27],"popularity":0.2091,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/1N0MeXwNFJKIn4A89ftgWRkz2cD.jpg","release_date":"1991-08-01","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Anna Göldin, letzte Hexe","original_language":"de"},{"id":273166,"adult":false,"title":"O Teri","video":false,"overview":"Prantabh and Anand, associated with a news channel in Delhi, are in search of a big scam to prove a point to their senior. A dead body accidentally lands up in their car.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.3446,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/8yDmeoOKcWtp0TU9n66hAfVAqy3.jpg","release_date":"2014-03-28","vote_average":2.2,"backdrop_path":"/qSeMx4F9dqinXuNqlg1QNBMuKzy.jpg","original_title":"ओ तेरी","original_language":"hi"},{"id":465634,"adult":false,"title":"Sindoor","video":false,"overview":"Laxmi is half of a famous singing couple when both her relationship and career are destroyed by the jealous plotting of her husband , Vijay. Years later, Laxmi is widowed and raising a stepdaughter, Lalita, when Vijay returns to the scene to meddle in her new family's affairs and once again threaten her domestic happiness.","genre_ids":[10751,18],"popularity":0.3612,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/1yTKMQaz1LHeQbJhzs17H8bRYj5.jpg","release_date":"1987-07-31","vote_average":3.5,"backdrop_path":"/5llxS1Lz4J5gLE40sDUZUW6yyZ9.jpg","original_title":"Sindoor","original_language":"hi"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt3863552","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q18603021","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"278899","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/bajrangi_bhaijaan"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148539,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"Sydney","type":1,"iso_639_1":"hi","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2015-07-15T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"M"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"GB","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"hi","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2015-07-17T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"12A"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2016-05-26T00:00:00.000Z","certi